{"tid":559407,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"《The Division》角色被貓貓亂按刪除！Ubisoft 神回：忍耐別刪除貓","createTime":"2018-02-13T06:56:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-13T07:15:02.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9d659710202acbc8929d99dcbea6457d2e457250","tid":559407,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T06:56:50.000Z","msg":"有養貓貓的朋友都會發現，貓貓很喜歡躲在一些奇奇怪怪的地方，尤其是冬天的時候，就喜歡躺在暖暖的電腦上，鍵盤亦是貓貓十分喜歡的位置之一。然而有時候貓貓一躺下去，電腦入面的資料就糟糕了。近日有《全境封鎖（The Division）》的玩家，就因爲自家貓貓躺了鍵盤結果打了很久的角色竟然被刪除了，而結果卻十分出乎意料！<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2005000/2006934/cat02-_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2005000%2F2006934%2Fcat02-_1024.jpg&h=7b512992&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2006934/《全境封鎖》角色被貓貓亂按刪除！Ubisoft%20神回：忍耐別刪除貓\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2006934%2F%E3%80%8A%E5%85%A8%E5%A2%83%E5%B0%81%E9%8E%96%E3%80%8B%E8%A7%92%E8%89%B2%E8%A2%AB%E8%B2%93%E8%B2%93%E4%BA%82%E6%8C%89%E5%88%AA%E9%99%A4%EF%BC%81Ubisoft%2520%E7%A5%9E%E5%9B%9E%EF%BC%9A%E5%BF%8D%E8%80%90%E5%88%A5%E5%88%AA%E9%99%A4%E8%B2%93&d=hJwxMhAxtaGs%2B0tgGmBkLUzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=a925ee2a\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2006934/《全境封鎖》角色被貓貓亂按刪除！Ubisoft%20神回：忍耐別刪除貓</a>"},{"pid":"97908c3de0551a58812b79454db0ca36f05e5053","tid":559407,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T06:58:47.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2005000/2006934/cat6_600.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2005000%2F2006934%2Fcat6_600.JPG&h=55d4581a&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n事緣有《全境封鎖》玩家向 Ubisoft 表示，自己在去廁所的時候，自家貓貓站到自己的鍵盤上。結果，因爲「誤觸」按鍵而令到《全境封鎖》的角色被刪除了。樓主附上一張無辜貓貓的照片給 Ubisoft，希望能夠將帳號恢復。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2005000/2006934/cat4_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2005000%2F2006934%2Fcat4_600.jpg&h=dfb04389&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"c6db34028e7ed8d6c4c38ede4a4e14dcc9628c99","tid":559407,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T06:59:23.000Z","msg":"想不到，今次 Ubisoft 在幾日内就很快回復，表示「非常重視您的案件」、以及「您的貓身安全」，更神回應說「請你耐心等候並按耐您刪除貓的衝動」。其後更在 Ubisoft 官方《全境封鎖》的直播節目提起整件事，表示貓貓看似知道自己做錯事，無辜的樣子很好笑。Ubisoft 最後幫樓主恢復了角色，並將整件事放到 Facebook 官網上分享。<br />\n<br />\n樓主其後到 Facebook 專頁留言，開心表示「天地有正氣」，因爲 Ubisoft 不但幫他恢復了角色，更「在遊戲周報中幫我公開譴責那隻叛變的貓咪」現在他終於可以成功歸隊繼續做特工打機。"},{"pid":"f17f70576198f84fcb91813079c42906b8ab51bd","tid":559407,"uid":5502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T07:15:02.000Z","msg":"仲有人玩???"}]}